<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>{% block title %}Artean, bolsa de empleo de Cuatrovientos{% endblock title %}</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    {% stylesheets
    '@CuatrovientosArteanBundle/Resources/public/css/artean.css'
    '@CuatrovientosArteanBundle/Resources/public/css/bootstrap.min.css'
    '@CuatrovientosArteanBundle/Resources/public/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css'
    filter='cssrewrite' output='css/compiled/app.css' %}
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="{{ asset_url }}">
    {% endstylesheets %}
    {% block extrastyles %}{% endblock %}

    {% block head %}{% endblock %}

</head>

<body>
<div class="container-fluid">
    <nav class="navbar navbar-toggleable-md navbar-light bg-faded">
        <button class="navbar-toggler navbar-toggler-right" type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
                data-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="#"><i class="fa fa-compass"></i> Artean</a>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
            <ul class="navbar-nav">
                <li class="nav-item active">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="#">Home <span class="sr-only">(current)</span></a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="#">Features</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="#">Pricing</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link disabled" href="#">Disabled</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid">
        <div class="container">
            <div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide">
                <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
                    <div class="carousel-item" >
                        <div>
                            <h1 class="cover-heading">Candidat@s</h1>
                            {% image '@CuatrovientosArteanBundle/Resources/public/img/astronaut.png' %}
                            <img src="{{ asset_url }}" alt="darest candidates" title="fearless candidate"/>
                            {% endimage %}
                            <p class="lead">Entra en tu perfil o crea una cuenta en Artean indicando tu email</p>
                            <form method="post" name="applicant"
                                  action="{{ path('cuatrovientos_artean_applicant_signin_save') }}">
                                <div id="applicant_sign_in">
                                    <div class="col-lg-offset-3 col-lg-6">
                                        <div class="input-group">
                                            <input class="form-control" type="email" id="applicant_sign_in_email" 1name="applicant_sign_in[email]" required="required"
                                                   placeholder="tudirección@decorreo"/>
                                            <span class="input-group-btn">
                                            <button class="btn btn-secondary" type="button"
                                                    onclick="forms.applicant.submit()">Entrar</button>
                                        </span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <!--button type="submit" id="applicant_sign_in_save" name="applicant_sign_in[save]">Alta en Artean</button></div><input type="hidden" id="applicant_sign_in__token" name="applicant_sign_in[_token]" value="dGrOXtN830u2L9kHR4r__oHOjd4uWEXW1syCgIqwYkY" /-->
                            </form>

                        </div>
                        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="next">
                            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                        </a>

                    </div>

                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                        <div>
                            <h1 class="display-3">Artean Cuatrovientos</h1>
                            <p class="lead">Desde Cuatrovientos queremos dar la bienvenida a todo el alumnado y empresas que por primera vez se acercan al instituto y a aquellos que continúan con sus programas formativos. </p>

                            <p class="lead">
                                <a href="#carouselExampleControls" class="btn btn-lg btn-success-outline" data-slide-to="0"><i class="fa fa-user"
                                                                                                aria-hidden="true"></i>
                                    Alta Candidatos</a>
                                <a href="#carouselExampleControls" class="btn btn-lg btn-info-outline"  data-slide-to="2"><i class="fa fa-building" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                                    Empresas</a>

                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                <div class="carousel-item" >
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="cover-heading">Empresas</h2>
                        {% image '@CuatrovientosArteanBundle/Resources/public/img/company.png' %}
                        <img src="{{ asset_url }}" alt="Join us, and together we will rule the galaxy"
                             title="Companies are welcome"/>
                        {% endimage %}
                        <p class="lead">Si eres una empresa puedes iniciar un proceso de selección o bien publicar una
                            oferta de empleo que llegue a nuestr@s candidat@s.</p>
                        <p class="lead">
                            <a href="{{ path('cuatrovientos_artean_open_offer_new') }}"
                               class="btn btn-lg btn-success-outline"><i class="fa fa-users" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                                Solicitud a bolsa</a>
                            <a href="{{ path('cuatrovientos_artean_open_offer_ad_new') }}"
                               class="btn btn-lg btn-warning-outline"><i class="fa fa-bullhorn" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                                Publicar oferta</a>
                        </p>

                    </div>
                    <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>




        </div>

    </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-3">
        <div>
